      <originalsloc id="aspace_a5ee5f475780c69092e74d4d03a938ad">
         <head>Existence and Location of Originals</head>
         <p>The entire collection can be located in the Gregory Breit Papers (MS 1465). The papers consist of correspondence, diaries, reports, data files, writings, printed material, and topical files relating to Gregory Breit's research and teaching career.</p>
         <p>HM 211 only consists of correspondence (1932-1973), diaries (1935-1973) and notebooks (1935-1973)</p>  
      </originalsloc>
